Every night after 10 pm, your "night safety" routine runs. This routine locks the door until the next morning at 6 am. The door is unlocked at 6am.

However, at 2 am, you're back from a night out with your friends, and you start the "back home" routine. This routine unlocks the door and turns on the foyer light.
